        Installation
        ------------
        
        Install contentrules.slack by adding it to your buildout:
        
            .. code-block:: ini
        
                [buildout]
        
                ...
        
                eggs =
                    contentrules.slack
        
        
        and then running buildout:
        
            .. code-block:: shell
        
                $ bin/buildout
        
        
        
